{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>水警人員到場將女子救起，事主獲救時昏迷，被送往藍灣半島，再轉送東區醫院搶救。警方正調查事主身份及墮海原因。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125040338700865536529416.jpeg/3pttID2D-LiYKrL6CgVQXOu3tgo_nal-Q24Z7mZuGe4\" alt=\"事主被送往東區醫院搶救。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>事主被送往東區醫院搶救。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125040341385351168193876.jpeg/8k_REqcPlkjgQi2B3ZYFnGheNPliFkHW0IghhvWIIYY\" alt=\"事主被送往東區醫院搶救。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>事主被送往東區醫院搶救。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125040767518117888369402.jpeg/JJrYOqOY3NZoGWbYFFMHotEULnUhWRTuuIIKw52CCsM\" alt=\"水警人員陪同送院。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>水警人員陪同送院。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210722/494833167740833792589063.jpeg/Itmw6ACLZkJkxZ7RFYqa6cj2BD7igzw5ClfrWApX61g\" alt=\"東龍洲。（漁護署「郊野樂行」網站圖片）\"><figcaption>東龍洲。（漁護署「郊野樂行」網站圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-26T04:13:51.885348+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":127,"images":4,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}